ay-block text-center\">\n	<figure class=\"remove-margin\">\n		<img class=\"size-auto\" height=\"120\" width=\"180\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/icons_box.png\" alt=\"Box Icons\">\n		<figcaption>Box Icons</figcaption>\n	</figure>\n</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:49;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Short Film\";s:4:\"text\";s:206:\"<a style=\"display: block;\" data-lightbox href=\"http://vimeo.com/15261921\" title=\"Vimeo Video\">\r\n	<img alt=\"Demo Image\" height=\"140\" width=\"200\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_mediaplayer.jpg\"/>\r\n</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:50;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Get Widgetkit\";s:4:\"text\";s:549:\"<a class=\"display-block text-center\" href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/blog/item/root/introducing-widgetkit\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"size-auto\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/widgetkit_icon.png\" alt=\"The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress\" title=\"The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress\" width=\"140\" height=\"130\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<p>The next generation tool set for Joomla and WordPress</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"button-more\" href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/blog/item/root/introducing-widgetkit\" target=\"_blank\">Visit Website</a></p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:51;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:7:\"Welcome\";s:4:\"text\";s:631:\"<p>Welcome to \"The Big Easy\", your online magazine about culture, nightlife, travelling and local events.</p>\r\n<p>Our team of journalists is in action all around the world to bring you all the hot stories, portraits and reports.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 55px;\">If you like our service, please spread the word on <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/yootheme\" target=\"_blank\">twitter</a>, <a href=\"#\">google+</a>, <a href=\"#\">facebook</a> or other social networks or use one of the buttons below.</p>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons plus\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons heart\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons eye\" href=\"#\"></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:52;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Social Icons\";s:4:\"text\";s:380:\"<ul class=\"social-icons\">\r\n	<li class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/yootheme\" target=\"_blank\"></a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"dribbble\"><a href=\"http://www.dribbble.com/yootheme\" target=\"_blank\"></a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"facebook\"><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\" target=\"_blank\"></a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"rss\"><a href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/rss/\" target=\"_blank\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:53;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Exhibition\";s:4:\"text\";s:430:\"<a data-spotlight=\"effect:fade;\" class=\"teaserimage\" href=\"index.php?page_id=33\">\r\n	<img height=\"240\" width=\"240\" alt=\"Demo Image\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_02.jpg\"/>\r\n	<div class=\"overlay\"></div>\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"module-title\">Exhibition</h3>\r\n<p>Next week opens an impressive exhibition presenting various stamp designs from Asia and Russia. </p>\r\n<a class=\"button-more\" href=\"index.php?page_id=33\"></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:54;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:11:\"The Goddess\";s:4:\"text\";s:438:\"<a data-spotlight=\"effect:fade;\" class=\"teaserimage\" href=\"index.php?page_id=33\">\r\n	<img height=\"240\" width=\"100\" alt=\"Demo Image\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_03.jpg\"/>\r\n	<div class=\"overlay\"></div>\r\n</a>\r\n<h3 class=\"module-title\">The Goddess</h3>\r\n<p>The legendary Citroën DS was known for its aerodynamic futuristic body design and innovative technology.</p>\r\n<a class=\"button-more\" href=\"index.php?page_id=33\"></a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:55;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Categories\";s:4:\"text\";s:502:\"<ul class=\"line-iconbig\">\r\n	<li class=\"glass\">\r\n		<h3>Night life</h3>\r\n		<p>We show you the hottest locations in your area.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"food\">\r\n		<h3>Food &amp; Cooking</h3>\r\n		<p>From \"fast and delicious\" to 6 course menus. Be inspired!</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"music\">\r\n		<h3>Music &amp; Culture</h3>\r\n		<p>There are many things happening around you! Let´s go!</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li class=\"fashion\">\r\n		<h3>Fashion</h3>\r\n		<p>Young and talented designers show their work.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:56;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"Cover Art\";s:4:\"text\";s:283:\"<a class=\"teaserimage\" data-spotlight=\"on\" data-lightbox=\"transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic;\" href=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_04_lightbox.jpg\">\r\n	<img src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_04.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" alt=\"Demo Image\" />\r\n</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:57;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"World Expo\";s:4:\"text\";s:283:\"<a class=\"teaserimage\" data-spotlight=\"on\" data-lightbox=\"transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic;\" href=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_05_lightbox.jpg\">\r\n	<img src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_05.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" alt=\"Demo Image\" />\r\n</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:58;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Restaurant\";s:4:\"text\";s:283:\"<a class=\"teaserimage\" data-spotlight=\"on\" data-lightbox=\"transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic;\" href=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_06_lightbox.jpg\">\r\n	<img src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/home_spotlight_06.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" alt=\"Demo Image\" />\r\n</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:59;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Social Icons\";s:4:\"text\";s:2607:\"<p>As a little extra, Big Easy theme offers a set of social icons. They are easy to add to your content and are part of our editable Adobe Fireworks Image Source Files.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"social-icons\">\r\n	<li class=\"rss\"><a href=\"#\">RSS</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"#\">Twitter</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"facebook\"><a href=\"#\">Facebook</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"flickr\"><a href=\"#\">flickr</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"#\">LinkedIn</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"myspace\"><a href=\"#\">myspace</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"lastfm\"><a href=\"#\">Last.fm</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"dribbble\"><a href=\"#\">Dribbble</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"digg\"><a href=\"#\">Digg</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"delicious\"><a href=\"#\">delicious</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"deviantart\"><a href=\"#\">deviantArt</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"technorati\"><a href=\"#\">Technorati</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"stumbleupon\"><a href=\"#\">Stumble Upon</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"yahoo\"><a href=\"#\">Yahoo</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"openid\"><a href=\"#\">OpenID</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"xing\"><a href=\"#\">Xing</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"forrst\"><a href=\"#\">Forrst</a></li>\r\n	<li class=\"googleplus\"><a href=\"#\">Google +</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a little code example how to add them:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;social-icons&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;rss&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;twitter&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li class=&quot;facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Possible class names are <strong>rss, twitter, facebook, flickr, linkedin, myspace, lastfm, dribbble, digg, delicious, deviantart, technorati, stumbleupon, yahoo, openid, xing, forrst</strong> and <strong>googleplus</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h1>Additional Icons</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>We added additional icons optimized for box, black and transparent module style. They are part of our editable Adobe Fireworks Image Source Files.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons plus\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons heart\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons eye\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n<a class=\"symbol-icons arrow\" href=\"#\"></a>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a little code example how to add them:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;a class=&quot;symbol-icons plus&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a class=&quot;symbol-icons heart&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a class=&quot;symbol-icons eye&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;a class=&quot;symbol-icons arrow&quot; href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Possible class names are <strong>plus, heart, eye</strong> and <strong>arrow</strong>.</p>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:60;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"List Iconbig\";s:4:\"text\";s:553:\"<p>This theme comes with a special list style called \"line-iconbig\". Create an unordered list with the class \"line-iconbig\" and add the following classes to the &lt;li&gt;s:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"line-iconbig\">\r\n	<li class=\"glass\"><h3>Glass</h3><p>&lt;li class=&quot;glass&quot;&gt;</p></li>\r\n	<li class=\"food\"><h3>Food Icon</h3><p>&lt;li class=&quot;food&quot;&gt;</p></li>\r\n	<li class=\"music\"><h3>Music Icon</h3><p>&lt;li class=&quot;music&quot;&gt;</p></li>\r\n	<li class=\"fashion\"><h3>Fashion Icon</h3><p>&lt;li class=&quot;fashion&quot;&gt;</p></li>\r\n</ul>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}','yes'),(88,0,'widget_rss','a:2:{i:2;a:0:{}s:12:\"_multiwidget\";i:1;}','yes'),(89,0,'timezone_string','','yes'),(90,0,'embed_autourls','1','yes'),(91,0,'embed_size_w','','yes'),(92,0,'embed_size_h','600','yes'),(93,0,'page_for_posts','0','yes'),(94,0,'page_on_front','30','yes'),(95,0,'default_post_format','0','yes'),(96,0,'@@TABLE_PREFIX@@user_roles','a:5:{s:13:\"administrator\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Administrator\";s:12:\"capabilities\";a:62:{s:13:\"switch_themes\";b:1;s:11:\"edit_themes\";b:1;s:16:\"activate_plugins\";b:1;s:12:\"edit_plugins\";b:1;s:10:\"edit_users\";b:1;s:10:\"edit_files\";b:1;s:14:\"manage_options\";b:1;s:17:\"moderate_comments\";b:1;s:17:\"manage_categories\";b:1;s:12:\"manage_links\";b:1;s:12:\"upload_files\";b:1;s:6:\"import\";b:1;s:15:\"unfiltered_html\";b:1;s:10:\"edit_posts\";b:1;s:17:\"edit_others_posts\";b:1;s:20:\"edit_published_posts\";b:1;s:13:\"publish_posts\";b:1;s:10:\"edit_pages\";b:1;s:4:\"read\";b:1;s:8:\"level_10\";b:1;s:7:\"l